articles.title: 3 U.S. Marines killed, 5 seriously injured after Osprey crash in Australia - The Washington Post
articles.description: The MV-22B Osprey was carrying 23 U.S. Marine Corps personnel when it crashed Sunday off the coast of Darwin, in Australia’s Northern Territory, officials said.

articles.title: US military personnel in Australia air crash, no deaths reported - Reuters
